# Snap2Calendar

A colorful, playful web app that converts chat screenshots into Google Calendar events instantly.

🔗 **Live App:** [https://snapshot-to-sync.lovable.app](https://snapshot-to-sync.lovable.app)

## How it works
1. Upload a screenshot of a conversation
2. AI extracts the meeting details automatically
3. Click "Open in Google Calendar" to create the event

No login required. No sign-up needed.

## Tech Stack
- React + TypeScript + Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Gemini Vision AI for extraction
- Google Calendar link generation
